messages.subject: Weird Al and Donny Osmond....
messages.msgSnippet: This is a video of Danny Osmond and Weird Al dancing to the ENTIRE song in front of a green screen. Much more than the snippets that are shown in the video. I
messages.messageBody:
"This is a video of Danny Osmond and Weird Al dancing to the ENTIRE
song in front of a green screen. Much more than the snippets that are
shown in the video. I always thought it was a blue screen, not green.
Donny Osmond is a very good sport, in my opinion."

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GWc6QQ9JlMc&feature=related

This was hilarious. I have seen Weird Al more times than I can count at the
Orange County Fair. He really is amazing. I will show this video to Drew
when he wakes up.

I saw Donny Osmond in concert when I was about 10 at the Southern California
Girl Scout Diamond Jubilee Roundup at Glen Helen. Thousands of tween girls
swooning... :)

Cindy
